{"tid":1255491,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[由連登核心推出社區] 落地落區谷集合","createTime":"2019-06-24T13:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T15:50:51.000Z","uid":58041,"like":108,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"d3656b3156693e19e633508e488f9dfe549bad55","tid":1255491,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:48:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">以下係連登仔全力將連登思想推出去社區<br />\n落區做實事既區谷既tg links</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">目標：</span><br />\n宣傳626馬拉松請願<br />\n落區/傳單/以一傳十救民意 既落地谷<br />\n（原本既反送中18區谷仍然存在，而呢堆新谷係executional groups)<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">請以不影響民生為首要，事關今日圍稅局連我呀哥都有微言</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">分區落地理念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">分區前：</span><br />\n<br />\n依家係一部分連登仔全部塞晒上係連登上面做宣傳<br />\n引至內容泛濫，只有同一堆人同緊同一堆人互相宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">分區後：</span><br />\n<br />\n唔再局限係連登宣傳<br />\n變成由全連登人行出一步向其他媒體/落社區宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">分區必要性</span><br />\n例如我個區會有我個區先知既facebook group仔/傳單好地方<br />\n只有開到行動小區ssss先有地方真正傾executional level details<br />\n同傳單小組係同一概念<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點搞法？</span><br />\n想幫手既人請做兩步<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 入626落區公海</span><br />\n公海：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JwAW2lf2pLT4UlGBJCIkew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJwAW2lf2pLT4UlGBJCIkew&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=0dcc431b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JwAW2lf2pLT4UlGBJCIkew</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 揀自己個區傾社區滲透Execution</span><br />\n（傳單、落區、分區落地媒體宣傳）<br />\n依家未有太多人，請入左落區公海先<br />\n<br />\n東區：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JwAW2ld7WMVC9tpTs4kZpA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJwAW2ld7WMVC9tpTs4kZpA&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=967a7d7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JwAW2ld7WMVC9tpTs